			        <br>&nbsp; Level Select -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Highlight password at the options menu, then hold Select and press Triangle, L1, Square, release Select and press Triangle, L1, Square, Triangle, L1, Square</font>&nbsp;<br>
